originalText.text:
Ordered a sink from Sears who uses 123stores.

It came with the wrong faucet holes. And it was confirmed by Sears with a call to 123stores that it came with the pedestal as pictured. In addition the the dimensions stated 20 wide x 26 long x 38 high.

This came sink only no pedestal wrong faucet holes. I have been trying for a week to return this. No response. SEARS can’t reach 123stores. No phone number is shown for 123 stores.

This was hands down the worst online retail experience I had for the last 10 years or more.
